---
title: Spicy Thai-Style Vegan Grain Salad with Tomato, Cucumber, Scallions & Peanuts
description: Bold Thai-inspired flavors take this grain and veggie salad to the next level! A sweet and spicy dressing brightens up up a mix of fresh greens, cucumber, tomato, and our hearty grain blend. Top with toasted peanuts, fried onions, and crispy wonton strips for a colorful meal that hits the table in a speedy 20 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6765a5319bfc6de73c8e1d52-761e7f4e.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/6765a5319bfc6de73c8e1d52-en-US.pdf
